Diversity & Inclusion
IPG is increasing diversity and forging a culture of inclusion. We take this commitment seriously and are leader on this issue. Read More





 
Our Leadership
The men and women who lead Interpublic are dedicated, experienced and forward-thinking. We come from all backgrounds and walks-of-life. Read More





 
IPG Gives Back
Our role as a corporate citizen takes place at many levels throughout the company. Our initiatives support corporate responsibility, volunteerism and involvement in our local communities. Read More







 
Sustainability
A sustainable IPG is one where our business practices are in line with social and environmental concerns and our workplace is an inclusive and diverse one. STRONGER chronicles our sustainability and corporate citizenship efforts. Read More





 
Corporate Governance
Our board of directors and our policies ensure we are accountable to all of our stakeholders - investors, clients and employees, around the world. Read More





